transforma.rosmsg

类 InspectionResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • transforma.rosmsg.InspectionResult
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    RosBridgeListener

    public class InspectionResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements RosBridgeListener
    This is a singleton class of inspection result that only creates itself when the inspection starts It's created to store relevant numbers relating to inspection result. Check whether the Inspection result attribute is null or not to determine whether there is an ongoing inspection. Making inspectionResult null pointer is necessary when an inspection finishes. Adding & Removing RosBridgeListener is necessary to prevent error occuring
